  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p747069/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>【台本】</strong></p>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\tI <u>wish</u><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">①&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">I wasn't afraid all the time but... I am.</span></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<u>People</u><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">②&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">should not be afraid of their governments. Governments should be afraid of their people.</span></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\tThose caught in <u>violation</u><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">③&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">of </span><u style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">curfew</u><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">④&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">will be prosecuted without </span><u style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">leniency</u><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">⑤&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">or exception.</span></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\tIt's past curfew<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">, you know.</span></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\tHelp me!!</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\tHave mercy!</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\tOh, not tonight.</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\tWho are you?</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\tGentlemen, I want this terrorist found, and I want him to understand what terror really means.</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<u>We're working on several leads</u><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"><u>.</u></span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px;\">⑥</span></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\tHer parents were detained when she was twelve.</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\tIt was like those black bags erased them <u>from the face of the earth.</u><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">⑦</span></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\tMummy!</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\tYou have one chance. You must tell us the whereabouts of <u>code name V</u>.⑧</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\tIf our own government was responsible for the deaths of a hundred thousand people... would you really wanna know?</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\tPlease!</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\tThose who are responsible <u>will be held accountable</u><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">⑨</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">.</span></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\tThe time has come for you to live without fear.</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\tI'm ready.</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\tThis country stands <u>on the edge of</u><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">⑩&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"><u>oblivion</u></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">⑪</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">,</span></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\tI want everyone to remember why they need us.</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\tKill him.</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\tMy turn.</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\tI somehow have this feeling that everything was connected.</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\tWe're all part of it.</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\tAre we ready for it?</div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\tThe only <u>verdict</u><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">⑫&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">is <u>vengeance</u></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">⑬</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">.</span></div>\n<p>\n\t<strong>【语言点讲解】</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">①</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">WISH= </span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">这个动词后面跟过去式（或&quot;would&quot;）:&quot;I wish I wasn't afraid.&quot;（我希望我不会害怕。）</span></p>\n<p>\n\t②PEOPLE= <span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">在这句台词中，第一个&rdquo;people&ldquo;指的是&ldquo;人&rdquo;，最后一个&ldquo;people&rdquo;指的是&ldquo;民族&rdquo; （因为一个民族社会是由个人群体组成的）。所以第一个词是复数，第二个词是单数。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t例句：</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">1- People here are very nice ( 1 person, 2 people)&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">这里的人们都很友善（1个人用&ldquo;person&rdquo;,2个人用&ldquo;people&rdquo;）</span></p>\n<p>\n\t2- My people wants more freedom. All the peoples in the world need peace.&nbsp;<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">人民群众都想要更多的自由。全世界所有民族都需要和平。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t③VIOLATION= <span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">Transgression（违反）（打破，违反纪律）</span></p>\n<p>\n\t④CURFEW= <span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">指在某一个时间后禁止人们在街道上活动的一项禁令。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">⑤</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">LENIENCY=</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">（比较正式的用法）宽大处理。&quot;Lenient&quot;的反义词是&ldquo;harsh, strict&rdquo;(严格)</span></p>\n<p>\n\t⑥WE'RE WORKING ON SEVERAL LEADS= We have several lines of investigation; we are investigating different possibilities.</p>\n<p>\n\t⑦FROM THE FACE OF THE EARTH= <span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">如果某些东西从地球表面上清除掉的话，那他们就消失了（可能被杀掉了），而且不可能再找回来。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t⑧CODE NAME V=&nbsp;<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">一个代号叫&ldquo;V&rdquo;的人。单词&ldquo;V&rdquo;（等于罗马字符中的&ldquo;5&rdquo;）指的是11月5号（盖伊&middot;福克斯被执行死刑的日子)。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t⑨WILL BE HELD ACCOUNTABLE= <span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">如果你对某事&ldquo;held accountable&rdquo;的话，那就要对这件事有责任，并要因此付出代价。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t⑩ON THE EDGE OF= <span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">跟某物非常近，非常接近。。。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t⑪OBLIVION= <span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">（正式用法）遗忘。如果某物&ldquo;falls in oblivion&rdquo;，那么它就被遗忘了，而且没有人记得它。在这里，总统害怕人们忘记了他们是多么地需要政府。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t⑫VERDICT= <span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">由法官或陪审团宣布的判决，判定一个犯人有罪与否及对其采取的处罚。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t⑬VENGEANCE= <span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">复仇（</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px;\">Revenge）</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">。意大利语的&ldquo;复仇&rdquo;是&quot;vendetta&quot;。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 12px; line-height: 25.2px;\">声明：本文系Angel Castano老师授权沪江</span><a class=\"creatLinks\" href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/tag/%E8%8B%B1%E8%AF%AD/\" style=\"border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dashed; border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 90, 148); color: rgb(0, 90, 148); text-decoration: none; font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 12px; line-height: 25.2px;\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"更多英语内容\">英语</a><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 12px; line-height: 25.2px;\">独家</span><a class=\"creatLinks\" href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/ifans/\" style=\"border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dashed; border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 90, 148); color: rgb(0, 90, 148); text-decoration: none; font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 12px; line-height: 25.2px;\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"更多翻译内容\">翻译</a><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 12px; line-height: 25.2px;\">，转载请注明出处。本文仅代表作者个人观点，仅供参考。如有不妥之处，欢迎指正。</span></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p747069/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p747069\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p743298/\">英语学习精华：别说你懂新概念！（上）</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p746915/\">最强历史顾问：唐顿粉英国女王爱给剧挑BUG</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p745209/\">十大奇葩面试问题，你要怎么回答？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p747102/\">2015美剧女星收入排行：“大爆炸”佩妮领街</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p747045/\">观影指南：看《碟中谍5》之前必知的6件事！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 